<a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=168313>Geylan's Profile</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub21.ezboard.com/uskace.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Skace</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 10<br> <font color=#F0E68C>(5/28/02 5:49:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/feqtestregistryfrm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=531.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Armor Question !</span><hr size=1> HP and AC are both important.<br><br>But, AC can cap. If you cap your AC, you try to put your HP through the roof as high as possible without hurting your AC.<br><br>HP will always help, but some mobs will hit you for max no matter what your AC is. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#292929><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub21.ezboard.com/uankhal.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Ankhal</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 11<br> <font color=#F0E68C>(5/28/02 12:38:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/feqtestregistryfrm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=531.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Armor Question !</span><hr size=1> AC is proberably the most important since it allows you to avoid being hit and taking less damage when you are hit.  However, a larger amount of hps is great when tankin mobs that are way above your lvl and will hit for a lot no matter what.  Also the more hitpoints you have the more efficiant Complete Healing is.  You do want to cover both area's as much as possible but for your everyday tanking I still say AC. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#333333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub21.ezboard.com/ufiresofeternity.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fires of Eternity</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#F0E68C>(6/9/02 4:51:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/feqtestregistryfrm14.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=531.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_question_mark.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Armor Question !</span><hr size=1> pre AC cap:<br><br>AC..HP........Sta..Str.....The Rest<br><br>post Ac cap:<br><br>HP....Sta..Str....The Rest........AC<br><br> <p><center><table cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tr><td valign=centre><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=119758 target=_blank><img src=http://www.btinternet.com/~spican3000/pic.jpg border=0 alt="Lilee'Vreck - Vah'Shir Bard"><br><img src=http://www.btinternet.com/~spican3000/nameplate.jpg border=0 alt="Lilee'Vreck - Vah'Shir Bard"></a></td><td align=center valign=top><td align=center valign=top bgcolor=#000000><a href=http://pub72.ezboard.com/bscarab14802 target=_blank><img src=http://www.btinternet.com/~spican3000/scarab.jpg border=0 alt="Member of SCARAB"></a><br><a href=http://guildless.com target=_blank><img src=http://www.btinternet.com/~spican3000/pixel.jpg border=0 alt = "Guildless"></a></td></tr></table>Lilee the Psycho Bard</center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#292929><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub21.ezboard.com/usilayntest.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Silayn Test</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 14<br> <font color=#F0E68C>(6/9/02 5:29:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub21.ezboard.com/feqtestregistryfrm14.sh